    <data key="d0">Kainos: Kainos Advances Patient Care with Next Generation Interoperability Platform</data>
    <data key="d1">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4WjXH8Wp0E4</data>
    <data key="d2">A multi-tenant microservices architecture designed to normalize siloed healthcare data into the FHIR standard and provide clinicians with a unified longitudinal view of patient health records. Serves over 650,000 patients and 10,000 health care workers.</data>
    <data key="d3">interactive, control, data_ingestion</data>
